short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Checks webpages for California Proposition 65 warnings

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Detects if there are any California Proposition 65 warnings on any webpage that you visit.

If a Prop 65 warning is detected on a website, the icon changes to a caution sign. Tap the icon to highlight and scroll to the warning(s).

Note: Depending on the site code, behavior, or other factors, the extension might not be able to detect any or all Prop 65 warnings on some pages. Please use at your own discretion.
